text.__SUMMARY__: Dioon angustifolium is a species of cycad that is endemic to Tamaulipas and Nuevo León, Mexico.
text.Distribution:
Plants occur in two main areas:
the Sierra Madre Oriental and the Sierra de San Carlos, Sierra Tamaulipas
low hills in the vicinity of Soto la Marina, Tamaulipas
